This is a Free Chatgpt Detector Tool. Detect chatGPT content for Free, simple way & High accuracy.

A simple extension for detecting ChatGPT text , or Openai Text or any other AI text from your PC, Mac, and Windows.

The 'Chatgpt Detector - Free Ai Content Detector' extension is a simple Google Chrome extension that enables users to detecting ChatGPT text , or Openai Text or any other AI text from their Windows or Mac computer.


How to Use?

📭 Step 1: Firstly, click on the extension icon after installing it. Then click the 'Chatgpt Detector' icon button. 

🧑‍🎨 Step 2: Then, Copy text from any source , then paste to "Enter Text Here" Text field Box.

🧑‍🎓 Step 3: Then, Click The "Detect" Button.

Boom!!! You will see the percentage of the ai content within few second.

Features:

👍 ChatGPT 3.5 Text Detector and ChatGPT 4 Text Detector
👍 OpenAI Text Ai detector
👍 Easy To Use
👍 Simple and lightweight.
⭐️ Compatible with Google Chrome browser on PC, Windows, and Mac.
🔐 Respects user privacy 100%.
🆓 Forever free to use.
👍 Easily accessible with just one click from any tab.

First, install this extension. Then, click on Chorme extension icon, You will see a field to add your text for check. Simply add it here and click the "Detect" button. After that, you will see the result. Enjoy!!

The ChatGPT Detector for Windows extension works seamlessly with all your favorite websites!
